// Dragnet [Container]: dragnet-container-2026-2721 — Vulnerable Base Image Pull
// Status: deprecated | Level: critical | ID: 30a7865f-d188-5db0-bfe4-393cb0308c5d

any where
  (process.executable like~ "*amazonlinux:1*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:11*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:12*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:13*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:14*" or process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:18.04-ESM*" or process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:20.04-ESM*")
